Strum the chords in the last verse:

[G]L[F]et me watch ni[Am]ght fall on the river,
[G]t[F]he moon rise up and tu[Am]rn to silver,
[G]t[F]he sky move, the[Am] ocean shimmer,
[G]t[F]he hedge shake, the last living rose
[Am]qu[C]iver.[C][F]

